&lt;/div>&lt;/figure>
&lt;/p>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>In the &lt;code>TextField&lt;/code>, provide the URL of the &lt;code>index.json&lt;/code> file that specifies the location of the subsequent catalogs, for instance, the public Kaoto catalog can be used:
